Package io.nem.symbol.sdk.model.transaction

Interface JsonHelper

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonHelperGson, JsonHelperJackson2
    public interface JsonHelper
    JSON Helper interface used by the mappers to process json objects. Mappers should use the statically typed open API generated DTOs when possible. This helper should be used when there is no way of just using the DTOs. For example when processing "anyOf" kind of attributes. This interface hides the json underline implementation like gson or jackson2.
